Steps to follow

1. Go to the microsoft learn website - https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/
2. Click on training tab or use this link - https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/
3. Scroll down to search for different learning paths and modules.

In order to get the certification exam for free, follow these steps

1. Go on this link - https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/trainingdays/azure
2. Register for virtual training day
3. Attend the session
4. After that you will get a coupon code. You can avail that to get the 99 dollars exam for free.
